data.description: Located in well-maintained Hidden Creek subdivision, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath residence is perfect for you. There's NO HOA and at 1468 square feet, it's just the perfect size. The sellers have painted the interior, put in new flooring and shower in the master bedroom and it is ready for your enjoyment.  The level, well landscaped yard allows you to enjoy outdoor cooking on the patio with great views. You just need to jump in the car and head over here fast because this one won't last long. First come, first served. Don't miss your blessing!
